just twist that and take off, or you use this

00:03:02.499 --> 00:03:09.850
little like dial to change pedal assist modes
one: economic, two: standard, and three: high

00:03:09.850 --> 00:03:11.310
power.

00:03:11.310 --> 00:03:12.400
So that's just really cool.

